lead_paragraph: Steve Kerr, who last season became the first rookie head coach in 33 years to win an NBA title, has quickly transformed a Golden State Warriors team that was once a laughingstock into one that could dominate for years to come.

headline.main: Kerr Changed Fortunes of Long-Suffering Warriors
headline.print_headline: Kerr Changed Fortunes of Long-Suffering Warriors
